WEBVTT

00:00.069 --> 00:02.136
previously
on <i>ghost whisperer.</i>

00:03.524 --> 00:04.958
how come you
can see me and they can't?

00:05.023 --> 00:06.457
that's a long story.

00:06.524 --> 00:07.791
there's
a better place for you.

00:12.624 --> 00:15.190
well, that means
there's someone else
out there...

00:15.257 --> 00:17.491
like me?
i know!

00:17.557 --> 00:18.824
it's the 5 signs.

00:18.891 --> 00:20.624
the dead dove
on the doorstep.
the bee.

00:20.691 --> 00:22.331
the writing
on jim's back.

00:23.006 --> 00:24.273
the dead will walk.

00:24.340 --> 00:26.707
and now, the forgotten
have returned.

00:26.772 --> 00:27.707
wait, so, all 5 of
those things have happened.

00:27.772 --> 00:28.973
not the writing
on your back.

00:29.039 --> 00:30.173
it was latin.

00:30.186 --> 00:31.752
it translates to,
"death of a loved one."

00:36.471 --> 00:37.520
what is this?

00:37.521 --> 00:39.087
what are you doing
with all these spirits?

00:39.154 --> 00:41.087
we're getting ready.
for what?

00:41.154 --> 00:42.154
for what's coming.

00:43.284 --> 00:45.839
he's been planning this
for quite some time.

00:48.440 --> 00:50.939
no, this is
bigger than just him.

