01:22.838 --> 01:23.972
hey!

01:52.605 --> 01:54.371
you shouldn't be here.

01:55.040 --> 01:57.007
why not?

02:08.443 --> 02:10.162
this is your fault.

02:16.999 --> 02:18.266
no.

02:31.333 --> 02:32.333
yeah?

02:32.400 --> 02:34.133
hey, sorry,
i got lonely.

02:34.199 --> 02:35.932
everybody's healthy
in grandview tonight.

02:37.050 --> 02:37.773
i got no work.

02:37.774 --> 02:40.173
i can't believe
i have a week of this.

02:40.240 --> 02:41.840
what time is it?

02:41.906 --> 02:44.073
4:10.

02:44.140 --> 02:45.673
delia!
what?

02:45.740 --> 02:47.373
i have to call you back.

02:56.130 --> 02:57.063
hello?

02:57.410 --> 03:00.143
it's melinda,
i'm so sorry.

03:00.653 --> 03:02.234
what time is it?

03:02.235 --> 03:04.336
10 after 4:00.
i'm so sorry,

03:04.402 --> 03:07.302
i just--
i need to know
that you're ok.

03:07.369 --> 03:08.603
well, i'm not.

03:08.669 --> 03:09.636
you're not?

03:09.703 --> 03:11.402
no, i'm awake
at 10 after 4:00.

03:11.469 --> 03:12.869
why are you
doing this to me?

03:12.936 --> 03:14.202
ok, i'm--i'm sorry.

03:14.269 --> 03:15.302
go back to sleep.

03:15.369 --> 03:18.102
ok, wait,
are you ok?

03:18.169 --> 03:19.102
i'm fine.

03:19.169 --> 03:20.536
forget i called.

03:20.603 --> 03:21.536
all right,
good night,

03:21.603 --> 03:23.836
 good morning,
 good bye.

